Package gr.scriptum.eprotocol.wserver

Interface Summary
EProtocolWebService Dispatcher Interface for eProtocol Web Service Client.
 

Class Summary
ProtocolInfo The information requested from a ProtocolQuery message.
ProtocolMessage The input message to Web Service method receiveProtocol().
ProtocolQuery The request message to inquire about a previously submitted protocol message.
ProtocolReceipt The Receipt returned from receiveProtocol() method.
ProtocolWebService The Web Service to implement the eProtocol subscription method.
WsDocument This is what a document looks like when a client needs to upload it by calling receiveProtocol() method
WsRequest The parent of all eProtocol WS Requests
WsResponse The head of all eProtocol Web Service Responses
